OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FA marine scientist has been named
OL,8,F'Admiral of the Manx Herring Fleet',
OL,9,Fin a historic tradition dating back to
OL,10,Fthe 1600s.
OL,12,FDr David Beard is the latest Admiral
OL,13,Fto take on the ceremonial role on the
OL,14,FIsle of Man, which is more than 400
OL,15,Fyears old.
OL,17,FIt has been reinstated after local
OL,18,Ffishermen started to catch herring in
OL,19,FManx waters again following a deal
OL,20,Fwith the UK governments in 2023 to
OL,21,Fallocate a quota.
