OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FIt is hoped that decision will lead to
OL,8,Fa commercially viable herring fishery
OL,9,Fin the island for the first time in 25
OL,10,Fyears
OL,12,FDr Beard said: "I am incredibly proud
OL,13,Fto take on this role which holds
OL,14,Fimmense historical significance. It is
OL,15,Fa real honour.
OL,17,F"The quota only became available due
OL,18,Fto the persistence and hard work of
OL,19,FDEFA, particularly the Sea Fisheries
OL,20,FManager, Jack Emmerson, with the full
OL,21,Fsupport of Minister Clare Barber.
