OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,F"I would also wish to recognise the
OL,8,Fefforts of the Manx fishing community
OL,9,Fin responding to the opportunity and
OL,10,Fcatching the herring quota within a
OL,11,Ffive-week period last summer.
OL,13,F"This is co-management at its best and
OL,14,Fa further example of the sustainable
OL,15,Fmanagement approach adopted by both
OL,16,FGovernment and the fishing industry
OL,17,Fwithin Manx waters."
