OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FTraditionally, the Admiral of the Manx
OL,8,FHerring Fleet was responsible for
OL,9,Fensuring that the island's farmers and
OL,10,Fboat owners followed the legal
OL,11,Frequirement to have their nets and
OL,12,Fvessels ready for the opening of the
OL,13,Ffishing season each year.
OL,15,FThey were also tasked with monitoring
OL,16,Ffishermen's conduct at sea with any
OL,17,Fmisdemeanours dealt with by a land-
OL,18,Fbased Water Bailiff.
