OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FAt that point in history, the herring
OL,8,Ffishery was a largely directed
OL,9,Factivity, almost like a military
OL,10,Foperation, to ensure food security and
OL,11,Feconomic prosperity.
OL,13,FNowadays, the support of the recently
OL,14,Freinstated Manx herring fishery is
OL,15,Fundertaken collaboratively between the
OL,16,FDepartment of Environment, Food and
OL,17,FAgriculture (DEFA) and the Manx Fish
OL,18,FProducers Organisation (MFPO), of
OL,19,Fwhich Dr Beard is the Chief Executive.
