OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FHowever, Dr Beard plays a significant
OL,8,Frole in ensuring Manx fisheries are
OL,9,Fsustainably managed by working with
OL,10,FGovernment to ensure regulations are
OL,11,Ffit for purpose.
OL,13,FClare Barber MHK, Minister for
OL,14,FEnvironment, Food and Agriculture,
OL,15,Fsaid: "The appointment emphasises the
OL,16,Fsignificance of the Manx fishing
OL,17,Frevival in recent years.
