OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,F"David's appointment is symbolic of
OL,8,Four efforts to preserve and
OL,9,Fsustainably manage our herring
OL,10,Ffishery, ensuring its prosperity for
OL,11,Fgenerations to come.'
OL,13,FDespite the herring fishery employing
OL,14,Fmore than 2,000 people at its peak in
OL,15,F19th century, the Admiral's duties
OL,16,Fslowly diminished and eventually
OL,17,Fceased altogether.
OL,19,F"Although it was briefly revived in
OL,20,Fthe 1960s and 1990s, nobody has held
OL,21,Fthe role for more than 30 years.
