OL,3,CAdmiral of the Manx Herring Fleet
OL,4,Cnamed - what is it and why does it
OL,5,Cexist?
OL,7,FLieutenant Governor, Sir John Lorimer
OL,8,Fsaid: "Dr Beard's appointment is a
OL,9,Ffitting way to celebrate the
OL,10,Freintroduction of herring quotas in
OL,11,Fthe Isle of Man and honour an
OL,12,Fimportant Manx tradition."
OL,14,FA new quota for langoustines is also
OL,15,Fdue to become available to Manx boats
OL,16,Fin 2024.
